est un délit.", "words": [4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9, 10]}, {"id": 2, "text": "DÉBATS ET OPINIONS", "words": [11, 12, 13]}, {"id": 3, "text": "E X ER", "words": [14, 15, 16]}, {"id": 4, "text": "ED Trouvez le nom correspondant aux verbes suivants.", "words": [17, 18, 19, 20, 21, 22, 23, 24]}, {"id": 5, "text": "1.", "words": [25]}, {"id": 6, "text": "Manifester 4.", "words": [26, 27]}, {"id": 7, "text": "Protester : 2.", "words": [28, 29, 30]}, {"id": 8, "text": "Se plaindre 5.", "words": [31, 32, 33]}, {"id": 9, "text": "Se disputer : 3.", "words": [34, 35, 36, 37]}, {"id": 10, "text": "Critiquer : 6.", "words": [38, 39, 40]}, {"id": 11, "text": "Reprocher :", "words": [41, 42]}, {"id": 12, "text": "ED Choisissez les termes possibles.", "words": [43, 44, 45, 46, 47]}, {"id": 13, "text": "1.", "words": [48]}, {"id": 14, "text": "On lui fait des", "words": [49, 50, 51, 52]}, {"id": 15, "text": "2.", "words": [53]}, {"id": 16, "text": "Cette entreprise a reçu beaucoup de 3.", "words": [54, 55, 56, 57, 58, 59, 60]}, {"id": 17, "text": "Il y a une erreur sur l'addition, ce n'est pas | ça | correct | mécontent", "words": [61, 62, 63, 64, 65, 66, 67, 68, 69, 70, 71, 72, 73, 74, 75, 76]}, {"id": 18, "text": "4.", "words": [77]}, {"id": 19, "text": "Je dis |des disputes | du bien| du mal | une plainte | de ma voisine.", "words": [78, 79, 80, 81, 82, 83, 84, 85, 86, 87, 88, 89, 90, 91, 92, 93]}, {"id": 20, "text": "5.", "words": [94]}, {"id": 21, "text": "Il n'est pas agréable de recevoir des disputes| critiques | reproches |", "words": [95, 96, 97, 98, 99, 100, 101, 102, 103, 104, 105, 106]}, {"id": 22, "text": "D Choisissez la bonne explication.", "words": [107, 108, 109, 110, 111]}, {"id": 23, "text": "1.", "words": [112]}, {"id": 24, "text": "« Non, l'addition est fausse, cela ne fait pas 47 € !", "words": [113, 114, 115, 116, 117, 118, 119, 120, 121, 122, 123, 124]}, {"id": 25, "text": "»", "words": [125]}, {"id": 26, "text": "a.", "words": [126]}, {"id": 27, "text": "plaint.", "words": [127]}, {"id": 28, "text": "b.", "words": [128]}, {"id": 29, "text": "Il est accusé.", "words": [129, 130, 131]}, {"id": 30, "text": "2.", "words": [132]}, {"id": 31, "text": "« Non à la réforme !", "words": [133, 134, 135, 136, 137, 138]}, {"id": 32, "text": "»", "words": [139]}, {"id": 33, "text": "a.", "words": [140]}, {"id": 34, "text": "Ils manifestent.", "words": [141, 142]}, {"id": 35, "text": "b.", "words": [143]}, {"id": 36, "text": "Ils se disputent.", "words": [144, 145, 146]}, {"id": 37, "text": "3.", "words": [147]}, {"id": 38, "text": "« Non, ce n'est pas vrai, je n'ai jamais dit ça !", "words": [148, 149, 150, 151, 152, 153, 154, 155, 156, 157, 158, 159]}, {"id": 39, "text": "»", "words": [160]}, {"id": 40, "text": "a.", "words": [161]}, {"id": 41, "text": "Elle fait un reproche.", "words": [162, 163, 164, 165]}, {"id": 42, "text": "b.", "words": [166]}, {"id": 43, "text": "Elle se défend.", "words": [167, 168, 169]}, {"id": 44, "text": "4.", "words": [170]}, {"id": 45, "text": "« Vous n'auriez pas dû lui téléphoner !", "words": [171, 172, 173, 174, 175, 176, 177, 178]}, {"id": 46, "text": "»", "words": [179]}, {"id": 47, "text": "a.", "words": [180]}, {"id": 48, "text": "fait une critique.", "words": [181, 182, 183]}, {"id": 49, "text": "b.", "words": [184]}, {"id": 50, "text": "Il fait un reproche.", "words": [185, 186, 187, 188]}, {"id": 51, "text": "5.", "words": [189]}, {"id": 52, "text": "« C'est vous qui avez volé mon portefeuille !", "words": [190, 191, 192, 193, 194, 195, 196, 197, 198]}, {"id": 53, "text": "»", "words": [199]}, {"id": 54, "text": "a.", "words": [200]}, {"id": 55, "text": "Il accuse.", "words": [201, 202]}, {"id": 56, "text": "b.", "words": [203]}, {"id": 57, "text": "Il proteste.", "words": [204, 205]}, {"id": 58, "text": "6.", "words": [206]}, {"id": 59, "text": "« Votre travail est excellent !", "words": [207, 208, 209, 210, 211, 212]}, {"id": 60, "text": "»", "words": [213]}, {"id": 61, "text": "a.", "words": [214]}, {"id": 62, "text": "Elle fait un compliment.", "words": [215, 216, 217, 218]}, {"id": 63, "text": "b.", "words": [219]}, {"id": 64, "text": "Elle se plaint.", "words": [220, 221, 222]}, {"id": 65, "text": "7.", "words": [223]}, {"id": 66, "text": "« Cet appareil ne marche pas !", "words": [224, 225, 226, 227, 228, 229, 230]}, {"id": 67, "text": "»", "words": [231]}, {"id": 68, "text": "a.", "words": [232]}, {"id": 69, "text": "|| manifeste.", "words": [233, 234]}, {"id": 70, "text": "b.", "words": [235]}, {"id": 71, "text": "Il est mécontent.", "words": [236, 237, 238]}, {"id": 72, "text": "ED À vous !", "words": [239, 240, 241, 242]}, {"id": 73, "text": "Parlez de votre culture.", "words": [243, 244, 245, 246]}, {"id": 74, "text": "1.", "words": [247]}, {"id": 75, "text": "Les manifestations sont-elles fréquentes ?", "words": [248, 249, 250, 251, 252]}, {"id": 76, "text": "Dans quel contexte ont-elles lieu ?", "words": [253, 254, 255, 256, 257, 258]}, {"id": 77, "text": "2.", "words": [259]}, {"id": 78, "text": "Dans quelles situations est-il courant de faire des compliments ?", "words": [260, 261, 262, 263, 264, 265, 266, 267, 268, 269]}, {"id": 79, "text": "3.", "words": [270]}, {"id": 80, "text": "Dans le contexte professionnel, comment fait-on des critiques ?", "words": [271, 272, 273, 274, 275, 276, 277, 278, 279]}, {"id": 81, "text": "Sont-elles directes ou plutôt diplomatiques ?", "words": [280, 281, 282, 283, 284, 285]}, {"id": 82, "text": "4.", "words": [286]}, {"id": 83, "text": "Vous-même, comment faites-vous des reproches ou des critiques ?", "words": [287, 288, 289, 290, 291, 292, 293, 294, 295]}, {"id": 84, "text": "5.", "words": [296]}, {"id": 85, "text": "Faites-vous volontiers des compliments ?", "words": [297, 298, 299, 300, 301]}, {"id": 86, "text": "Dans quelles circonstances ?", "words": [302, 303, 304, 305]}, {"id": 87, "text": "Tests 290 à 292} cent soixante-sept + 167", "words": [306, 307, 308, 309, 310, 311, 312, 313]}]}